data.description: Great home with vaulted ceiling in Great room.  Wonderful Fireplace.  Huge back yard that backs to walking trail.  All the bedrooms are large.  There is also a huge area upstairs that can be used for storage, or would be a fun kids play area.  The A/C is new.
